SUMMARY:Information: MILDMAY LINE: Monday 29\, Tuesday 30 June\, Wednesday 
 1 and Thursday 2 July\, after 2345 each evening\, no westbound service 
 from Camden Road to Willesden Junction. The 2359 and 0015 services from 
 Stratford will terminate at Camden Road. Use London Overground services 
 from Euston to Willesden Junction\, Northern line from Camden Town\, or 
 local bus routes 1\, 24\, 46 88 and 214 from Camden Road / Camden Town.
END:VEVENT
